{"title":"潮汕功夫茶（外一首）","authors":["刘少敏"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":3,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"潮汕功夫茶（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘少敏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远客来潮汕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请尝功夫茶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚烫的情高冲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浓厚的意低洒＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斟满小茶盅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡谊诚无价"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一轮明月落壶中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泡出一夜开心话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"品茶  如品潮汕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山水有灵气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日月孕精华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淳朴乡风百姓家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊高冲、低洒均为潮汕功夫茶讲究的方法。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潮州弦诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妙韵指尖生乡音弦上流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹拉弹拨有板有眼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迷人的“尺工六”＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋风雁落平沙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春日狮戏彩球＊＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢快处龙翔凤翥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哀怨处山悲水愁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵  多少乡情在此中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫怪岁岁年年听不够"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊“尺工六”为传统记谱符号。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊＊潮州音乐中有《平沙落雁》、《狮子戏球》两个曲目。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}